# Decisions

This directory indexes decision records for `<repo-name>`.

## Belongs Here

- adopted documentation-structure decisions
- decision rationale and tradeoffs
- records of why a repository-docs change was chosen

## Does Not Belong Here

- current canonical guidance: `../Architecture/`
- open alternatives still under discussion: `../Proposals/`
- rollout checklists and cutovers: `../Migrations/`
- retired material kept only for record: `../Archive/`

## Use

Use this subtree for durable records of what was decided and why.
